Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.06,0:00:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your call can not be connected at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave a message after the beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about tonight's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:21.04,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:24.71,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open your window, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come no matter what, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be fun! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:27.29,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what are {\i1}you{\i0} do{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that out of the blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so viole{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Just open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.83,0:00:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand when you open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.90,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get ready, so I'll come over in half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.14,0:00:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You look so cute, Taiga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, come over here and check her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, you look amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, it's the perfect size.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it okay for me to borrow these clothes from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not borrowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're yours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name "R. Aisaka" is sown inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this is your father's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just sort of left it because it didn't fit him, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wearing his cast-offs? Are you messing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want it, I'll just throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These small chores really suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one who told me to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Destroy the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you say something like that when you can't even say your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Girl Ya-chan will cast some magic on you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now don't go too wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the party starts,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this will smell really good mixed in with your scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, Ryuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my father's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, when I ran away from home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:04:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a few valuable things with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.28,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means this is my grandfather's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stolen goods?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you'll a catch a cold like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:16.77,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Write down your name and class when you enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, there are a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many are here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. There's only one important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you have to do tonight, get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Yuri-chan-sensei, you dressed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the reason you're not coming to the party is because you have a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to a course for single women about buying real estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real estate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm going to buy an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why today, of all days?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:05:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's because women who date on\NChristmas Eve are far from being prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you find something you want, you have to get it right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I need to worry about buying an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.06,0:05:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, try to stay out of trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness the Christmas tree was fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades went up too, so I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be rewarded for all the effort you put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and you'll definitely get what you want as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fantastic single life is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you all for coming out tonight for this party, planned by the God of Broken Hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:51.75,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We went through a lot of trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kitamura's clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:55.75,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}but regardless, this Christmas party is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, we'll lose if you complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:06:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I truly appreciate your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you all to have a wonderful time tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to celebrate Christmas Eve, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.35,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Drumsticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called turkey, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just normal chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of home-bred turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanako, they have cake over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corner over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara in hot pants and Nanako-san in an innocent one piece are really hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, why is everyone all dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look out of place... I mean, poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep focused while you're walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The floor will get sticky if syrup spills on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why I didn't see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I couldn't stand how the drinks were being handled, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I'm surprised you have such an expensive suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that chicken grease on your hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taka-chan, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, it's home-bred turkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:29.78,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, you're so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.47,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen Ami-chan yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I caught a glimpse of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! Was she hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was she really hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Taiga too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Taiga isn't bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}He's right, where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:55.57,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm all in for Ami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan and Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.99,0:08:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When exactly did they practise for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Kushieda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.65,0:09:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about tonight's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.50,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.89,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open your window, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come no matter what, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.89,0:09:52.47,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be fun! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan and Taiga were both hot, but still cute as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you planning to stay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was different than your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, "hot, but still cute", and so on, are basically the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Then, am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hot, but still cute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hot! You're really hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn perverted exhibitionist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maruo, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm hot, but still cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me some fruit punch please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow it turned out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how was my singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you practise for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't kept a secret, it wouldn't have been a surprise, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was totally caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where's Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could tell she tried her best,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to give her some fruit punch as a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.95,0:11:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to Minori-chan's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was going to get Minori to come here and then go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something about welcoming Santa, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but maybe there's something she'd rather not see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I gave you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I think you should stop playing this childish game of house."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why do you have to pretend to be daddy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't even listen to me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To give everyone a happy and joyful Christmas,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm prepared to take off one or two\Npieces of clothing, or even take it all off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be part of the happy, glittering scene on Christmas Eve,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}while wearing a happy face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu, can you get me some fruit punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I burned too many calories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji is waiting for you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he won't leave until he sees you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's even prepared to live at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's not that you don't like him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're best friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, it doesn't work if I'm only good around Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's no Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll be alone this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also be alone next year...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and forever and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never have someone to rely on,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:13:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one to rely on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from my bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.26,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Santa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd approve!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would be the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa praised my Christmas tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is real, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, my dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...very much, Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't take it off, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, where did you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed it from a guy who was wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what did you do with your suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I traded it with the guy who was wearing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll definitely get it back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You took it off when it was just about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're honestly stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I planned everything for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you had the chance to meet Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to believe in Angel Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin is on her way to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you can still make it if you hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already changed my clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't want to leave you by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake Santa and faking being good... It was a fun experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and of course, I'm looking forward to tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.94,0:17:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If by some chance things go well with Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tomorrow's Christmas meal will be on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chicken and rice bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beef and rice bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.09,0:17:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we can't have chicken because of Inko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it'll just be a beef and rice bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.80,0:17:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry up! Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not there at that party, it'll mean I lied to Minorin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I said wai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa came already, so I have to be good until the end of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...just let me be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting Minorin to go to the party is my real Christmas present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, indecisive dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to give this back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always relying on Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On his kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those times have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin will definitely fall for Ryuuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Ryuuji truly likes Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they both like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I won't be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stay by Ryuuji's side anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to walk by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one beside Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji... Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't bring my cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my present is still in the pocket of the suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great bear, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.73,0:20:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kushie{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.62,0:20:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but let me speak first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.13,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.71,0:20:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we were at Amin's villa during the summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we had a talk one night about weird things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was about UFOs and ghosts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Takasu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About UFOs and ghosts.... I really think I shouldn't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be best not to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about it a lot recently, and this is what I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for just saying what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda will be leaving first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.70,0:21:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected by Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I close my eyes, I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you're dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.43,0:23:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already hearing her usual cheerful voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, boom!
